title: Multics and how people use systems

Been spending quite a bit of time on Multics work here at Bell Labs. It’s an ambitious system—very general, lots of moving parts. There’s interesting work in terminals and communications as well. I keep thinking about how people actually use these systems day to day, not just how they’re designed on paper.
